thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Michelle

author: Michelle
title: Michelle
text: My puppy was in so much pain and I called Ocean County Vet. they were kind and helpful Simply Wonderful! He Examined my puppy and diagnose him without charging me a fortune. I am and my puppy are 100% happy with the staff there. If you are looking for a Vet please consider this Office You will be very happy :) Thank you from Babalou....Woof! Woof!
